Log in without a password or any other credentials. <br>
Just enter your "handle", the name you want to be known by, and you're in.<br>
<br>
From any other device, do the same thing! You will be logged in automatically.<br>
<br>
This is done by using a combination of session cookies, client-stored private keys,
and hash-based client fingerprints. <!-- and operator oversight --><br>
<br>
In every case, you have the option to remain anonymous or to use a name of your choosing. Your private information, <br>
such as your phone number, email address, and name, is not required unless you choose to reveal it of your own volition.<br>
<br>
We hope you find this place welcoming and safe.